  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 36bccf2d2c1763242ba11eb36cdffde2, type: 3}
  m_Name: PlayerStatsBook
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  pages:
  - text: "Player stats\n\nPlayer stats describe the hero\u2019s core abilities and
      have a direct impact on combat, exploration, and how challenges are solved.\n\nStrength
      represents physical endurance and melee combat ability. It affects maximum
      health points, damage dealt with fists and melee weapons, and the ability to
      handle heavy objects. High Strength increases survivability and effectiveness
      in close combat.\n\nDexterity represents reflexes and physical agility. It
      affects the chance to dodge incoming attacks, the ability to open mechanical
      locks using lockpicks, and the number of Action Points (AP) available during
      combat. High Dexterity allows the character to avoid damage more effectively,
      perform more actions each turn, and react faster in combat situations."
  - text: "Characters with Dexterity 1\u20133 have 3 AP, Dexterity 4\u20137 have
      4 AP, and Dexterity 8\u201310 have 5 AP.\n\nPerception represents awareness
      and precision. It affects the chance to hit with firearms as well as the chance
      to land critical hits that deal increased damage. High Perception allows the
      character to strike targets more accurately and deal powerful, precise attacks
      more often.\n\nTechnical represents technical knowledge and the ability to
      operate devices. It affects the chance to successfully repair equipment, recover
      parts from damaged machines, open electronic and code-locked doors, and access
      special technical dialogue options."
  actions: []
